		<article id="comment-65652" class="comment-block">
			<header class="comment-header">
				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/5c919d80b054d6eefffe8d79cf2fef24?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">Susu</cite>
